\begin_layout Standard
There is a buyer who wishes to maximize the value of services received by
 a given parcel of land over two time periods.
 The land parcel has two possible states (developed and conserved) and the
 decision to develop a parcel of land is irreversible.
 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citet
key "arnold2013adverse"

\end_inset

