\begin_inset Formula $\ubPriv$
\end_inset

 with certainty -- either because the buyer offers exactly 
\begin_inset Formula $\ubPriv$
\end_inset

 and the landowner accepts or because the buyer offers 
\begin_inset Formula $\offer<\ubPriv$
\end_inset

